{
  "text": "Some researchers approximate the third grade fluid equations in a porous half space; for example, Ahmad [CITATION_1] by applying the Homotopy analysis method, Kazem et al. [CITATION_2] by applying the radial basis functions collocation method, Parand and Hajizadeh [CITATION_3] by applying the modified rational Christov functions collocation method, Baharifard et al. [CITATION_4] by applying the rational and exponential Legendre Tau method. For satisfying the boundary conditions, we satisfy the Eq. (14) as follows:",
